Class CBORToken<TValue>

java.lang.Object
com.authlete.cbor.token.CBORToken<TValue>
Type Parameters:
TValue - The type of the value of the CBOR token.
Direct Known Subclasses:
CTBoolean, CTBreak, CTByteString, CTIndefiniteOpener, CTNull, CTNumber, CTOpener, CTSimpleValue, CTTag, CTTextString, CTUndefined
public abstract class CBORToken<TValue> extends Object
CBOR token that the CBOR tokenizer (CBORTokenizer) constructs.
